body.name: VINGLI Tall Metal Storage Cabinet with Locking Doors and 4 Adjustable Shelves, Black Mobile Storage Cabinet Tool Cabinet with Pegboard for Garage, Gym, Office, Classroom, Utility Room,32Wx17Dx72H
features: 【Spacious Storage Space】Double packaging carton with metal corner protectors to protect the product from bending. Ship in 1 boxes! Featuring 4 adjustable shelves, you can adjust the height of each panel yourself depending on the items you need to place to maximize the storage space of the cabinet

【Multi-functional Lockable Doors】VINGLI metal cabinet has lockable doors with 2 keys, which will keep all your belongings secured. The extra built-in pegboards with hooks are helpful to declutter your garage tools or office sundries. The locking handles and magnet devices are friendly to users

【Excellent Load-bearing Capacity】With a strong and durable metal frame, this steel storage cabinet allows you to store heavy garage instruments up tp 150lbs per shelves(750lbs in total). It is perfect for office, garage, gym, workshop, classroom, utility room, etc.

【Heavy-duty Wheels】4 detachable and lockable rubber wheels make it easy to move around or stop somewhere. Easy and smooth to roll even fully loaded without scratching your floors. Available in mobile or freestanding as you wish

【Worry-free Warranty】Come with a straight forward written instruction and necessary tools for easy assembly, the assembly will be very clear. BTW, an electric screwdriver is recommended. It measures 32"Wx17"Dx72"H upon assemble. VINGLI is always here for you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It’s very sturdy and it’s movable which is very important because it’s against the wall where my water heater is behind it. Pretty easy to put together. Shipped separately by 2 days but that’s ok

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Update after 3rd one: Great value and ordering another
reviews.reviewText: Update after 3rd one:The first 2 arrived with damage boxes but the parts were not damaged. The 3rd cabinet had two prices that where bent in the large box (it comes in 2 boxes). It was mishandled badly during shipping because the factory packaging was all done correctly.The seller’s customer support was GREAT! They always got back within same day or 24 hours.I contacted them before fully unpacking because I didn’t know if they would want it returned and there was no way I could repackage it once it was all out. They said to go ahead and unpack it and that I would not need to return it if it was damaged.I sent them plenty of pictures of the unpacking process to show it was damaged upon receipt. They sent an entire new big box of parts. Sadly, it also had a few damaged parts but I was able to use pieces from both boxes to get a while I damaged cabinet.After having these 3 for a few months, they are great. I love the wheels, reinforced shelving, color and locking doors. I could not find all features on any cabinets at my local stores.I would but a forth if needed!——————————————Original review:Just put it together and will order a few more. The packing was well done and there were no dents on panels. This was my biggest concern but they’ve done a good job designing the packing. There are even metal corner protectors on each box corner and it comes in two boxes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well worth the money.
reviews.reviewText: Was easy to assemble, will hold a lot of stuff. Almost as strong as Gladiator Storage cabinets. I know for I have owned both of these cabinets over the years. I am 76 yrs old and I assembled these 2 I bought and they roll easily around the garage and will hold the weight of heavy tools & large gallons of antifreeze, windshield washer fluid etc. on their shelves with no problem.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 31, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality, sturdy
reviews.reviewText: We purchased two of these. They are very sturdy, made with good quality materials. While assembly was not easy, they went together well, no real problems. Note, however, that one of the door pins was defective and an alternative need to be rigged. Also, note that the caster plates had to fit in under the side wall bottom flanges in order to be seated correctly - This part had to be pryed out slightly with a screwdriver to accomplish this. But overall, we are very pleased with these cabinets. The fabrication is very good, and they were well-packaged for shipment.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Excellent except latch won’t work
reviews.reviewText: The cabinet was fairly easy to assemble. This is a high quality product and looks nice. I’m very pleased with the cabinet. But, the locking rod does not line up with the pre-drilled holes on the bottom. Appears that the rod, which is hidden by metal and there is no access, is missing an alignment tab or something. I requested a new door.The company responded by asking if I could repair the locking rod. They explained how to do it, I did it. The company offered me a $50.00 refund. I’m very happy with their solution.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Birthday gift for my son. He is very happy with it, lots of storage space. Keeps his garage tidy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best cabinet out there!
reviews.reviewText: I literally looked for a year or more for something like this. I needed something to store my vacuums and Bissell crosswave in. I don’t have a specific cleaning closet in my home. Almost every other cabinet I looked at had a permanent shelf right in the middle and you couldn’t put tall items like vacuums in them. This one has all shelves that are adjustable. I ended up putting two shelves in each one, high enough so my vacuums would fit under the shelves.I ordered two of these. They came super quickly. They both arrived in perfect condition! They were packed super well. My husband and I put them together fairly quickly. Very high quality and I have nothing bad to say about them at all. I put them in my garage and so glad I went with these since they have casters as well!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Ok Cabinet - Assembly is work
reviews.reviewText: Took a while for one person to assemble. Arrived in two boxes, three days apart.Quality seems normal. Some of the instructions weren't the easiest to follow.
